text: Maciej Jewtuszko (born January 31, 1981) is a Polish mixed martial artist who most recently competed in 2019. A professional since 2005, he has fought in the UFC, WEC, and KSW. He is the former KSW Lightweight Champion. == References == Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Polish sportspeople Category:Mixed martial artists Category:People from Szczecin
